徒刑，得併科新臺幣一千五百萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c552%2c20211125%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,訴,552,20211125,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"552","JDATE":"20211125","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}